#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:92
msgid ""
"The review will be performed by one of our expert legal translators. Our "
"translators translate exclusively into their native language (source "
"language). Once the review is complete, the entire document is reviewed by a "
"project manager from our team. Our project managers have legal training and "
"verify the compliance of the translation with the source document."
msgstr ""
"The review will be performed by one of our expert legal translators. Our "
"translators translate exclusively into their native language (source "
"language). Once the review is complete, the entire document is reviewed by a "
"project manager from our team. Our project managers have legal training and "
"verify the compliance of the translation with the source document."

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:94
msgid "Special cases"
msgstr "Special cases"

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:95
msgid ""
"1° For now, automatic quotes generated by Lexa do not calculate possible "
"repetitions between documents. Feel free to ask our team for an adjusted "
"quote by replying directly to the email you received."
msgstr ""
"1° For now, automatic quotes generated by Lexa do not calculate possible "
"repetitions between documents. Feel free to ask our team for an adjusted "
"quote by replying directly to the email you received."

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:97
msgid ""
"2° Automatic quotes generated by Lexa are calculated based on normal "
"delivery time. If your project is urgent, feel free to ask our team for an "
"adjusted quote by replying directly to the email you received."
msgstr ""
"2° Automatic quotes generated by Lexa are calculated based on normal "
"delivery time. If your project is urgent, feel free to ask our team for an "
"adjusted quote by replying directly to the email you received."

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:100
msgid "Delivery of your documents"
msgstr "Delivery of your documents"

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:101
msgid ""
"Unless you specify otherwise, your reviewed documents will be made available "
"on the portal."
msgstr ""
"Unless you specify otherwise, your reviewed documents will be made available "
"on the portal."

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:103
