"Validation of this quote implies full and complete acceptance of the general "
"terms and conditions of LEGAL 230, available at this link"
msgstr ""
"Validation of this quote implies full and complete acceptance of the general "
"terms and conditions of LEGAL 230, available at this link"

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:108
