#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:110
msgid "\"Approved for the amount of XXX excl. tax\"."
msgstr "\"Approved for the amount of XXX excl. tax\"."

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:113
msgid "Payment terms"
msgstr "Payment terms"

#: legal/templates/quote_template.html:114
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Upon receipt of the invoice, the payment term is %(payment_days)s days. It "
"is possible to invoice your client directly if the conditions are met to "
"proceed in this way (valid contact details, email address, purchase order). "
"Any amount not paid on its due date will automatically generate late "
"interest equivalent to three times the legal interest rate of the current "
"year as well as payment of an amount of %(recovery_fee)s %(currency_symbol)s "
"due for recovery costs. In all cases, you will receive an order confirmation "
"email. We sincerely hope that this proposal meets your expectations. We "
"would be very happy to assist you and remain at your complete disposal to "
"answer any additional questions you may have."
msgstr ""
"Upon receipt of the invoice, the payment term is %(payment_days)s days. It "
"is possible to invoice your client directly if the conditions are met to "
"proceed in this way (valid contact details, email address, purchase order). "
"Any amount not paid on its due date will automatically generate late "
"interest equivalent to three times the legal interest rate of the current "
"year as well as payment of an amount of %(recovery_fee)s %(currency_symbol)s "
"due for recovery costs. In all cases, you will receive an order confirmation "
"email. We sincerely hope that this proposal meets your expectations. We "
"would be very happy to assist you and remain at your complete disposal to "
"answer any additional questions you may have."

